      h2.title klog 
        span.silver helps you to keep track of your projects

      p klog is designed to be a districuted issue tracking and time management tool. as such, it should integrate with any distributed version control system. I use git, but klog is vcs agnostic - just track the files along with your code!

      h3 Get the code!

